    <main>
        <section>
            <h3>What's new in the latest update (version 0.5)</h3>
            <p>UI redesign with a new colour scheme, promotions added, 'about' quick link removed, newly developed restricted area semi-operational, past web versions now available for viewing and are still operational. This version also updates the UI of the update status of the website.</p>
        </section>
    </main>


    <footer>
        <p>whspace - Website version <span>0.5</span></p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        function toggleMode() {
            document.body.classList.toggle('light-mode');
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>